              <text>Section 19(3)(a) is amended by inserting <amend.in quote="1">and might be used by a judicial officer for the purpose of giving the accused a sentence indication</amend.in> after <quote.in quote="1">offender</quote.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 19(4) is amended by repealing paragraph (a) and substituting the following paragraphs:</text>
              <amend increment="1" quote="1">
                <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">a</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>advised the victim that—</text>
                    <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">i</label>
                      <para>
                        <text>it was for submission to the judicial officer sentencing the offender; and</text>
                      </para>
