                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">41</label>
                  <heading>Time for filing charging document</heading>
                  <prov.body>
                    <subprov skeleton="no">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes"/>
                      <para>
                        <text>Despite anything to the contrary in <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 22</citation></changeable> of the <changeable>Criminal Procedure (Reform and Modernisation) Act 2010</changeable>, the limitation period in respect of an offence against this Act ends on the date that is 2 years after the date on which the offence was committed.</text>
