                  <para quote="1">
                    <text><def-term id="DLM3361035">Judge</def-term> in relation to a District Court, or <def-term id="DLM3361036">District Court Judge</def-term> means a Judge who holds a warrant under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 5B</citation></changeable> of the District Courts Act 1947 to conduct jury trials</text>
                  </para>
