            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 243(5)(a) and (b): omit <amend.in quote="1">accused</amend.in> and substitute in each case <amend.in quote="1">defendant</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>New section 243A: insert after section 243:</text>
              <amend quote="1">
                <prov id="DLM3361039" irdnumbering="no" quote="1" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">243A</label>
                  <heading>Charges for money laundering</heading>
                  <prov.body>
                    <subprov skeleton="no">
                      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes"/>
                      <para>
                        <text>A person charged with an offence against section 243(2) or (3) or section 12B of the Misuse of Drugs Act 1975 in respect of any property that is the proceeds of a serious offence may be charged whether or not the person who committed that serious offence has been charged or convicted or is amenable to justice.</text>
